videos.description: Andrew Jones dishes to Kai Jones, who rises for the thunderous two-handed jam to extend Texas' lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Kai Jones skies for two-handed slam) 2020/12/6 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kai Jones skies for two-handed slam

videos.description: Jeremiah Robinson-Earl blows by Kai Jones and rises for a two-handed slam, plus the foul.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Robinson-Earl goes baseline for rim-rocking and-1 dunk) 2020/12/6 ESHEET

videos.headline: Robinson-Earl goes baseline for rim-rocking and-1 dunk

videos.description: Matt Coleman III drives through traffic and rocks the rim with the one-handed jam.

videos.headline: Coleman shows no mercy on the rim with emphatic slam

videos.description: Collin Gillespie picks off a Texas pass and advances the ball to Jermaine Samuels, who finds Jeremiah Robinson-Earl for the two-handed dunk to build Villanova's lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Gillespie's clutch steal leads to a Robinson-Earl slam) 2020/12/6 ESHEET

videos.headline: Gillespie's clutch steal leads to a Robinson-Earl slam

videos.description: No. 12 Villanova takes down No. 17 Texas behind Jeremiah Robinson-Earl and Justin Moore, who each score 19 points.
